[{"id":993716,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>如题^^</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/993716","replies":274,"created_ts":1700531997,"created":"09:59:57","title":"请分享一首或者一句你最喜欢的诗词！中外文不限","author":"Vvvv22","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Vvvv22","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1521/2add/655847_mini.png?m=1698732096"},{"id":993710,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"<p>刚从 win 阵营换成了 mac ，用了一周之后逐渐熟悉，有感而发。</p>\n<p>入手的二手 macbookpro(m1/16g)，对我日常 java/vue/react/小程序/app 开发、ps 简单图片处理、服务器数据库运维工作来说，m1 相对 intel11 代的提升是非常明显的，而且性能足够，多线程工作从来没有卡壳过，风扇很少转，配合 applewatch/airpods/iphone ，简直丝滑的不得了。</p>\n<p>可能是我追求太低，不过感觉 m2/m3 对我这种平平的程序员（非大数据/ai 工程师）来说实属过剩了。</p>\n<p>性能，够用就好，多出来的都是浪费。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/993710","replies":191,"created_ts":1700531511,"created":"09:51:51","title":"虽然现在 M3 了，但 M1 是真好用且够用","author":"x1024m","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/x1024m","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9189/6714/594345_mini.png?m=1673833196"},{"id":993690,"node":"随想","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/random","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_mini.png?m=1615956453","description":"<p>本来准备考完驾照，买买摩托车的。所以买了个电动车过渡用。\n配置如下，72V120A 的电池，2000w 电机，6000W 功率的控制器。\n骑了两个月，我已经不打算买摩托车了，优势如下：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>成本低，充满 9 度电，大概 4 块钱，可以跑 180 公里</li>\n<li>速度块，我都是走机动车道，以开汽车的标准走，跟着车流的速度，很安全。</li>\n<li>刹车性能优秀，这个我重点讲一下。我是松油门电流回收制动，我开到了最大。经过我测试，在各种雨水路面，都可以稳稳刹停下。由于前轮没有制动，所以丝毫不会失控。如果需要更短的制动，保持车把正，带前刹即可。我个人觉得，电机制动，比 ABS 还好使，后面看情况再给前轮加一个 ABS 就齐活了。目前后轮电机制动，我觉得可以吊打没有 ABS 的踏板了。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>实在想不出买摩托车的理由了。</p>\n<p>补充下：我摔过一次，下雨天的时候，前面的小车右转加油，我打方向，带刹车，直接摔车。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/993690","replies":160,"created_ts":1700529196,"created":"09:13:16","title":"大功率，大电池的电动车比摩托车香多了","author":"clacf1","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/clacf1","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b6808ae1bc9be74a53d9f6719c5122c2?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":993673,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1695370146","description":"<p>我和他矛盾爆发直接原因：</p>\n<p>1 、接口没有统一返回值；</p>\n<p>2 、前后端分离的项目，token 过期他直接重定向到首页而没有任何提示信息；</p>\n<p>3 、token 错误显示跨域错误，我怀疑压根没处理这种情况。</p>\n<p>和他争辩，说不过了就以修改时间不确定拖着。</p>\n<p>背景：</p>\n<p>1 、非互联网公司，公司开发就两个人，我和他，我不懂 Java ；</p>\n<p>2 、没有架构师、产品、设计人员，组织架构、开发流程很不完善；</p>\n<p>3 、leader 人不错，能力很强，但是不懂代码；</p>\n<p>4 、我前端一年经验，他后端 5 年经验。</p>\n<p>我对于他的看法：</p>\n<p>1 、他对 sql 优化确实有点东西，但他擅长 mysql ，公司用的 PostgreSQL ；</p>\n<p>2 、逃避复杂的东西（算法、后端架构系统性设计）；</p>\n<p>3 、和稀泥，脸皮厚；</p>\n<p>请问各位 v2 大佬：</p>\n<p>1 、碰到这种人你们怎么和他打交道？我是见都不想见到；</p>\n<p>2 、业务场景：一张表中 1000 万多的数据，每次查询需要扫描全表逐个计算过滤，拿到通过的数据，前端分页展示。对于该业务场景各位如何进行查询？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/993673","replies":149,"created_ts":1700518605,"created":"06:16:45","title":"后端老鸟耍不要脸","author":"ahhtree","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ahhtree","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ab15c8e8e60f09aeae477c629702d6b4?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":993697,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/993697","replies":114,"created_ts":1700530057,"created":"09:27:37","title":"电视家倒闭跑路了，还有能便宜看电视的 app 吗？","author":"duanxianze","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/duanxianze","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/add20ec4fadb6c65b87dd601f24f53a6?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":993823,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1692078075","description":"<p>上次发帖说( <a href=\"https://www.v2ex.com/t/991398\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.v2ex.com/t/991398</a> )，让帮忙测试狂发消息，却给我 oss 刷了 4.7TB 的流量。肉疼</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/drqJRpk.png\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/993823","replies":110,"created_ts":1700547708,"created":"14:21:48","title":"让帮我测试发消息，确给我 oss 刷了 4.7TB 的流量😭","author":"wkong","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/wkong","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5d93/cdb1/638625_mini.png?m=1692262962"},{"id":993910,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1695370146","description":"<p>OP 自身无车房贷，无孩子，已婚，目前互联网程序员年薪 50w 左右，已经干了 5 年多了，每天除了重复的工作，就是执行一些看起来毫无前途的 OKR （上级给的），挺痛苦的。</p>\n<p>毕业到现在一直在这一行，但纯打工接触到的东西太少了，比如商机的嗅觉、怎么调研、怎么拓客，十分缺失，就怕到 35 岁或者哪天社会不能接纳自己程序员的岗位时，我该怎么办，那会的压力应该比现在大的更多，孩子父母等等</p>\n<p>所以是否现在立马脱离苦海，出去看一看，实在不行再回来打工，大家怎么看呢？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/993910","replies":109,"created_ts":1700559607,"created":"17:40:07","title":"关于离职去寻找自身更多的可能性 ，比如做自媒体、电商、AI 工具等等；抛弃现在的几十万年薪，目的就是更深入发掘自己的潜能，大家怎么看？","author":"xujy1108","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xujy1108","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e81256187af61a095b9653a0330b32ad?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":993719,"node":"iPhone","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1630643991","description":"<p>双持的朋友请忽略 给父母买手机</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/993719","replies":107,"created_ts":1700532432,"created":"10:07:12","title":"5000 块是买二手 13pm 好 还是小米 14 好","author":"makaflow","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/makaflow","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bee6/803a/523771_mini.png?m=1700104669"},{"id":993692,"node":"JetBrains","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/jetbrains","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/2a9d/121c/912_mini.png?m=1582188474","description":"<p>一打开就吃了快 6g 的内存,项目都还没打开一半内存没了  </p>\n<p>特别是在开新项目建索引或者构建的时候,cpu 也是动不动就 100</p>\n<p>笔记本<br/>\ncpu: 8400<br/>\n内存: 16g<br/>\n系统: win10<br/>\nidea 版本: 20.3.3</p>\n<p>感觉硬件没有瓶颈啊,是版本问题吗</p>\n<p>百度找的 idea 优化的 vm 设置也没啥用</p>\n<pre><code># 堆栈设置\n-Xms4G\n-Xmx4G\n-XX:MetaspaceSize=1G\n-XX:MaxMetaspaceSize=1G\n-XX:+AlwaysPreTouch\n-XX:InitialCodeCacheSize=1G\n-XX:ReservedCodeCacheSize=1G\n\n# GC 参数\n-XX:ParallelGCThreads=4\n\n# JIT 参数\n-XX:+TieredCompilation\n-XX:CICompilerCount=4\n-XX:TieredStopAtLevel=1\n-XX:MaxInlineLevel=3\n-XX:Tier4MinInvocationThreshold=100000\n-XX:Tier4InvocationThreshold=110000\n-XX:Tier4CompileThreshold=120000\n\n-Djava.net.preferIPv4Stack=true\n-Djdk.attach.allowAttachSelf\n\n#Error and Dump\n\n# 关闭启动图片\n-Dnosplash=true\n\n-Dfile.encoding=utf-8\n-javaagent:C:\\Users\\Public\\.BetterIntelliJ\\BetterIntelliJ-1.16.jar\n</code></pre>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/993692","replies":100,"created_ts":1700529391,"created":"09:16:31","title":"idea 特别耗资源","author":"cMoon","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/cMoon","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6650/b2ac/595559_mini.png?m=1682666344"},{"id":993814,"node":"上海","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/shanghai","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_mini.png?m=1650127482","description":"<p>很严重，疼，不通气，打喷嚏\n每天早上憋醒疼醒的那种</p>\n<p>上海有没有那种中医可以看的\n对西药已经免疫了</p>\n<p>最好可以刷医保的</p>\n<p>🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/993814","replies":98,"created_ts":1700546455,"created":"14:00:55","title":"鼻炎患者求助贴🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏","author":"bugerbig","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/bugerbig","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a4c07fa154efed2a6df35702e7d94488?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":993720,"node":"分享创造","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1660301119","description":"<p>上周发布了一个帖子（<a href=\"https://www.v2ex.com/t/991317?p=2#reply194\" rel=\"nofollow\">原帖链接</a>），是自己开发的一款 Mac 系统休息提醒工具，<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/cn/app/%E4%B8%80%E4%BC%91-%E4%BC%91%E6%81%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%BC%9A%E5%84%BF/id6467176005?mt=12\" rel=\"nofollow\">App Store 地址</a>，感谢 @EricFuture @barfi1316 @947 等老哥提出宝贵意见，做了一次升级优化，新增了如下功能：</p>\n<h3>1 、休息前通知提醒</h3>\n<p>避免突然进入休息，有些突兀，默认在休息前 20s 进行了通知提醒，为了避免不必要的打扰，默认关闭了通知声音，也可以手动打开：\n<img alt=\"image.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/742903/1700529814249-b2768704-9c7a-4a9d-97ff-1c16a468e615.png#averageHue=%23e3e3e3&amp;clientId=ud456afab-1599-4&amp;from=paste&amp;height=121&amp;id=u037dbfa7&amp;originHeight=242&amp;originWidth=735&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=2&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=20336&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u215f4606-c20d-4600-a5fd-0d7d657a595&amp;title=&amp;width=367.5\"/>\n<img alt=\"image.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/742903/1700530018564-9aa8d68e-9cce-41d7-8a40-8f5f084db55d.png#averageHue=%23595959&amp;clientId=ud456afab-1599-4&amp;from=paste&amp;height=231&amp;id=u83f5e760&amp;originHeight=461&amp;originWidth=762&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=2&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=247614&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=ufca89340-6112-4026-a357-fd0ddb1c13e&amp;title=&amp;width=381\"/></p>\n<h3>2 、扩展显示器</h3>\n<p>休息画面默认会在所有显示器上展示，如果想“低调”一点的话，也可以只在主显示器上显示：\n<img alt=\"image.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/742903/1700529890687-3b23001c-78b0-4554-96a7-00eb8fa732a0.png#averageHue=%23e3e3e3&amp;clientId=ud456afab-1599-4&amp;from=paste&amp;height=56&amp;id=uf1a61a8b&amp;originHeight=111&amp;originWidth=756&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=2&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=11253&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u7a9f218e-56ed-4030-b0d8-ab51204800f&amp;title=&amp;width=378\"/></p>\n<h3>3 、屏幕镜像</h3>\n<p>有些朋友会有使用电脑投屏演示的场景，投屏时突然弹出休息界面不太友好，所以添加了投屏或镜像时自动暂停休息的选项（投屏结束自动恢复）。\n<img alt=\"image.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/742903/1700529793798-324d14a3-a12a-4a73-9d08-508b9691f935.png#averageHue=%23e3e3e3&amp;clientId=ud456afab-1599-4&amp;from=paste&amp;height=89&amp;id=u19a33774&amp;originHeight=177&amp;originWidth=747&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=2&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=17909&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u910924df-23ab-48ca-a813-cb90f62842e&amp;title=&amp;width=373.5\"/></p>\n<h3>4 、不可以跳过功能</h3>\n<p>当休息界面显示跳过按钮时，很多时候下意识的点击跳过，达不到休息的目的，目前休息界面不显示跳过按钮时已经禁用了 Command + Q 退出的快捷键，所以为了避免有急事时只能关机重启才能使用电脑的尴尬，加入了输入通关密码进行跳过的逻辑：\n<img alt=\"4.gif\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/gif/742903/1700529721737-7bfa9357-2a6e-48be-8b31-183372243d53.gif#averageHue=%23e0dfdb&amp;clientId=ud456afab-1599-4&amp;from=paste&amp;height=333&amp;id=uafa75097&amp;originHeight=665&amp;originWidth=1039&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=2&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=882068&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=ua9093d10-4e81-43a6-a214-a27b7d1af63&amp;title=&amp;width=519.5\"/></p>\n<h3>5 、自定义外观</h3>\n<p>可以手动切换深色和浅色模式，休息界面也会随之改变：\n<img alt=\"3.gif\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/gif/742903/1700529116240-c4920f4b-ce48-43f0-883a-8f00c0f16bf2.gif#averageHue=%23d5d4d1&amp;clientId=ud456afab-1599-4&amp;from=paste&amp;height=259&amp;id=u3159bda0&amp;originHeight=517&amp;originWidth=575&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=2&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=175537&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=uebf97c18-60bd-4167-ae6f-586a3a20870&amp;title=&amp;width=287.5\"/></p>\n<h3>6 、其它细节</h3>\n<p>当手动或自动暂停休息后，状态栏图标会显示眨眼动画，提醒用户休息已暂停。\n<img alt=\"6.gif\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/gif/742903/1700531374279-1038d1ac-64e6-4760-afc6-cd97eea264cd.gif#averageHue=%23e8e8e6&amp;clientId=ud456afab-1599-4&amp;from=paste&amp;height=147&amp;id=u11ae0b2a&amp;originHeight=294&amp;originWidth=542&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=2&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=516937&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u426a6e55-9de7-4e01-bc68-661d7f84cab&amp;title=&amp;width=271\"/></p>\n<h3>9 、抽奖</h3>\n<p>在评论区留下邮箱，总共 100 个兑换码，每天上午抽 20 个～</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/993720","replies":87,"created_ts":1700532572,"created":"10:09:32","title":"[抽奖送码] 感谢 V 站老哥对「一休」的支持和建议，新版更新，再抽 100 个～","author":"mengxianliang","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/mengxianliang","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2ee4/1f74/389923_mini.png?m=1699627842"},{"id":993733,"node":"游戏","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/games","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_mini.png?m=1611920927","description":"<p>我发现我玩很多游戏玩到中期就不想玩了，这是为啥</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/993733","replies":82,"created_ts":1700533411,"created":"10:23:31","title":"游戏玩不下去，怎么办？","author":"3059349417","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/3059349417","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fa6823ed4b2a1f3284c621815320e226?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":993741,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1692078075","description":"<p>最近在思考一个开源笔记类软件，它的版本控制应该怎么设计版本控制。突然想到 git 不正是我所需要的吗？</p>\n<ul>\n<li>有版本控制，细腻到文件级别</li>\n<li>格式开源，用户可控，遥遥领先  </li>\n<li>能 push 能 pull ，还能多节点备份  </li>\n<li>甚至能多用户协同</li>\n</ul>\n<p>最最重要的是，实现起来不会困难，简直就是完美的解决方案啊。</p>\n<p>当然，不会把命令行放在 UI 上让用户去输入，那样太硬核了，拿 git 简单包一包，应该也是不错的。  </p>\n<p>想做个调研，问问大家，如果你们用一款开源软件，它的版本控制哪种形式最好呢？</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1 ，Sqlite 数据库(db 文件)    </li>\n<li>2 ，定期全量 zip 归档   </li>\n<li>3 ，定期增量 zip 归档  </li>\n<li>4 ，git 版本控制  </li>\n</ul>\n<p>或者更多想法期望见到，谢谢大家</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/993741","replies":75,"created_ts":1700534137,"created":"10:35:37","title":"笔记类软件，内部用 git 实现版本控制，用户会喜欢吗？","author":"lstz","au